1
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:15,520
Sorry to trouble you, Mr. Yuwen.

2
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:16,600
Not at all.

3
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:17,680
General.

4
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,960
Miss, your voice sounds a bit weak.

5
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,040
Are your hands and feet cold?

6
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,560
Drinking some hot water should help.

7
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,120
That's an idea.

8
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:26,960
Stand up.

9
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:27,680
What's wrong?

10
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:28,760
What did you hear?

11
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,760
I just got here.

12
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:32,120
Miss, let's go.

13
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:35,840
For someone with such a wretched appearance...

14
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:37,760
...you shouldn't do even more wretched things.

15
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:39,320
I was monitoring a foreign spy.

16
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,600
It's part of my duty.

17
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,280
Don't cry.

18
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:31,560
Miss.

19
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:31,960
Miss.

20
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,520
You...

21
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,000
Seeing you cry like this...

22
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,520
I really...

23
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,680
I feel terrible.

24
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,720
Don't cry, don't cry.

25
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,080
I know.

26
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:41,840
You can't keep up the act, can you?

27
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,120
You admit you're a spy, don't you?

28
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,400
Crying means there's still hope for you.

29
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,680
But there's nothing I can do.

30
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,960
I will handle this impartially.

31
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:49,960
You foo...

32
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:50,560
Shut up.

33
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,960
I know what you want to say.

34
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:52,720
Whatever you have to say...

35
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:53,880
...go say it to the Lord.

36
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,680
Fine.

37
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,680
I also want to know

38
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,840
what the Lord thinks of someone like you,

39
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,520
a peeping tom who follows people to the toilet.

40
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,680
What his opinion is.

41
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:00,840
Disgusting.

42
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,400
So disgusting.

43
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:03,880
Miss.

44
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,400
Shameless.

45
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,120
Pervert.

46
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:08,720
To the toilet?

47
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,080
What does that mean?

48
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,480
Your Village rules...

49
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,720
...are quite interesting.

50
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,040
Tell me about them again.

51
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,520
Wei Qiaoge.

52
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,560
That's six times now.

53
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,880
Is it that hard to remember?

54
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,760
Has it been that many times?

55
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,440
Just tell me one more time.

56
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,720
It's just "no fighting."

57
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,480
Someone come quick!

58
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,600
I caught her!

59
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,920
Let go of me!

60
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,720
Don't move. Who did you catch?

61
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,640
Someone come!

62
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,960
Why is it you again?

63
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:19,760
Can you let go? Don't move.

64
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:20,360
I can't let go.

65
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:20,920
She'll run away.

66
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:21,880
Why run?

67
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,160
Where can she run to?

68
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:23,640
Don't move.

69
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,400
Be gentle.

70
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,800
Don't touch me.

71
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,200
You let go.

72
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:26,760
I won't.

73
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,480
Wei Long.

74
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:28,840
Wei Long.

75
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:29,720
What's wrong? What's wrong?

76
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,160
No...

77
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,000
Don't move.

78
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,520
Help me pry her off.

79
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,040
I can't pry her off either.

80
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,840
Miss Aqin.

81
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,280
Why don't you let go?

82
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:36,840
Let's talk nicely.

83
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,600
Right?

84
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,520
What are you doing?

85
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,200
Are you okay?

86
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,040
What's going on here?

87
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,840
She was weaving this.

88
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,600
Grass knot.

89
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,280
So it was you.

90
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,600
What are you weaving?

91
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,720
It's actually quite pretty.

92
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:05,680
Strategist.

93
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,760
Watch your boundaries.

94
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:07,960
Speak.

95
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,600
What's going on?

96
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,520
Speak properly.

97
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,600
You'll scare her.

98
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:13,200
What if she just found it?

99
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,160
No.

100
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,760
I wove it.

101
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,400
This kind of knot.

102
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,480
I remember it.

103
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:26,160
I know many people suspect me right now.

104
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,080
And are targeting me.

105
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,640
So I wanted to learn.

106
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,160
How to weave this kind of knot.

107
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,760
To help you catch the bad guys.

108
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,840
And to clear my name.

109
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,160
See? See?

110
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:35,960
What did I tell you?

111
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,920
Did you hear that?

112
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:39,080
She just wants to clear her name.

113
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,280
And help you catch the bad guys.

114
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,600
Alright, alright. She's helping you.

115
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,400
Just shut up.

116
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:42,840
Give it here.

117
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,400
This thing.

118
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,600
Can really catch them?

119
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,240
He can't see us even this close?

120
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,000
Seems his eyesight is bad.

121
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,480
So it really is related to him.

122
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,600
Then I can be cleared of suspicion, right?

123
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,280
Sure.

124
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:07,840
No.

125
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:10,720
Why?

126
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,160
Mr. Yuwen, you suspect me too?

127
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,080
No.

128
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,720
It only proves...

129
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,280
That he is connected to this knot.

130
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,480
But it doesn't prove...

131
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,920
Whether the spy among us...

132
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:21,200
Is the sender sending him messages...

133
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,040
Or the receiver obeying his orders.

134
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,280
Who cares about all that?

135
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,840
Just arrest him and interrogate him, and be done with it.

136
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,400
That's too rash.

137
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:37,960
What are you looking at?

138
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,200
I didn't understand it.

139
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,840
Who made this up?

140
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,400
Look.

141
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,680
Wei Long.

142
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,160
Enough.

143
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,720
Will you confess?

144
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,600
Confess to what?

145
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,480
Still stubborn.

146
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,280
Get him.

147
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,960
Who... who's being stubborn?

148
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,280
No, you didn't ask me anything.

149
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,840
You didn't ask, so what should I confess?

150
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,280
Did I not ask?

151
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,080
No, you didn't.

152
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,720
Are you here for a wedding or a funeral?

153
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,280
Are you a receiver or a sender?

154
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:13,520
What are you?

155
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:16,920
If you want to kill me, just do it.

156
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,640
Saying things I don't understand...

157
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,840
Are you trying to insult me?

158
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,280
You told me to ask him questions.

159
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,520
I asked, and you couldn't answer.

160
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,480
Get him.

161
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,160
What's wrong?

162
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:29,960
I can't watch this anymore.

163
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,160
Can we speak in private?

164
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:32,720
Okay, okay.

165
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,760
It is indeed too brutal.

166
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:35,640
But...

167
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,720
interrogating bad guys...

168
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,600
is always like this.

169
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,840
Don't be afraid.

170
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:41,920
Miss, what's wrong?

171
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:43,960
Mr. Yuwen.

172
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,400
From now on,

173
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,960
please call me Yu Tong.

174
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,160
Yu Tong?

175
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,640
That's a lovely name.

176
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,160
You remembered that your name is Yu Tong?

177
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,040
That's great.

178
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,160
What else did you remember?

179
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:58,840
It's okay, it's okay.

180
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,280
Take your time thinking.

181
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,520
You'll remember everything eventually.

182
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,320
I was wrong, I was wrong!

183
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,520
Just now... my attitude was bad.

184
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,520
I beg... I beg you!

185
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,840
Ask... ask me again!

186
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,720
What is your name?

187
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,040
She is called Yu Tong.

188
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,640
Yu Tong?

189
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:12,720
Aren't you He Qi?

190
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,520
Lying to me again?

191
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,720
I am He Qi!

192
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,400
Who is Yu Tong?

193
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,520
Who on earth is Yu Tong?

194
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,160
Besides,

195
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:19,760
what grown man

196
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,080
would have a name like Yu Tong?

197
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,480
It's just because it's too girly,

198
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,480
so you changed it to He Qi?

199
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,160
Is that it?

200
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,960
She is called Yu Tong!

201
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,760
She remembered her name!

202
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,160
She remembered!

203
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,720
Then are you still afraid when you see me?

204
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,440
I'm working on a case here.

205
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,960
You're messing up my train of thought.

206
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:38,840
Speak!

207
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:39,960
Who are you really?

208
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,840
I really am called He Qi.

209
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,160
I am a spy sent by the Daye Kingdom.

210
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,720
I have two underlings.

211
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,960
Called He Ba and He Jiu.

212
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,160
We saw you escorting a large vat.

213
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,440
We thought there must be treasure inside.

214
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,200
So we followed you all the way,

215
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,320
waiting for a chance to kill you and take the vat.

216
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,440
I came to scout for intelligence.

217
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:53,960
He Ba and He Jiu

218
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,600
are waiting in the bamboo forest two miles away.

219
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,360
I really am not called Yu Tong.

220
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,600
Where is the vat?

221
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:02,240
I swear we really didn't take the vat.

222
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,040
Darn it.
